kellwood <kwd> buying three companies
    st. louis, june 29 - 
kellwood co said it signed a definitive agreement to acquire robert
scott ltd inc, david brooks ltd inc and andrew harvey ltd of dedham,
mass. terms were not disclosed. combined sales of the three companies
in 1986 were over 50 mln dlrs, it said. the deals are expected to be
completed by july 31, kellwood said. reuter 
